1. *Duh* je u tom trenutku napustio moje telo. (The spirit left my body at that moment.)
2. Sanjam da letim kao *duh*. (I dream of flying like a spirit.)
3. On je bio pun *duha*. (He was full of spirit.)
4. *Duhovima* se obraćaš u molitvama. (You address the spirits in prayers.)
5. Ljudi često govore da *duh* postoji u svim stvarima. (People often say that a spirit exists in all things.)
6. Nisam osećala *duh* u toj sobi. (I didn't feel the spirit in that room.)
7. On je imao zamračen *duh*. (He had a dark spirit.)
8. Prepoznaćete *duh* slobode u njegovim očima. (You will recognize the spirit of freedom in his eyes.)